Package: teletool
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: arm64
X-TeleTool-Installer-Version: __INSTALLER_VERSION__
Maintainer: TeleTool Project <teletool@localhost>
Section: video
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/JohnDevAc/teletwat
Depends: adduser, alsa-utils, avahi-daemon, binutils, dtv-scan-tables, file, gir1.2-gst-plugins-bad-1.0, gir1.2-gst-plugins-base-1.0, gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0, gstreamer1.0-alsa, gstreamer1.0-libav, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, gstreamer1.0-plugins-base, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly, gstreamer1.0-tools, libc-bin, network-manager, python3, python3-fastapi (>= 0.100), python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, python3-pydantic (>= 2), python3-requests, python3-urllib3 (>= 2), python3-uvicorn (>= 0.30), sudo, tvheadend
Description: Tvheadend to NDI® and local-audio bridge for Raspberry Pi
 TeleTool provides a FastAPI Web UI and GStreamer bridge for sending
 Tvheadend services to NDI and local line-level audio outputs. This package
 includes the ARM64 GStreamer NDI plugin; the proprietary NDI SDK runtime is
 supplied separately through the guided Web UI upload page.
